text.tspan: We know multiplexer have many inputs and give single output, but we have to
decide which mutiplexer to use here.
As we have 3 variable function so we will use 3 - 1 = 2 selection which means
4x1 multiplexer in which 2 variables from A, B and C will be used as selection
If we have 4 variable function then 4 - 1 = 3 will be selection which means 8x1
multiplexer will be used and so on for other functions.
And if we have 'n' variable function then 2 x 1 multiplexer will be used
